defaultWith the potential introduction of a free biodegradable bag, we would need to consider the impact on our existing range of reusable bags. We would withdraw the existing ‘recycled and recyclable’
default 
defaultplastic bag as consumers would be unlikely to 
defaultpay a
default 5p 
defaultcharge if 
defaulta
defaultn alternative,
default free biodegradable bag 
defaultis available.
